extendedInfo.description: We made a Pinocchio of a funny picture puzzle.It can make children listen to the Pinocchio story by playing the puzzle.It has 6 levels, if you could solve the level within the given time you can go on to the next level.During your setting of the puzzle, you could have fun watching Pinocchio's nose grow.Please have your children have fun with this puzzle game that is good for developing the brain and improving concentration.keyword: puzzle, pinocchio, jigsaw, game
